     The question is, with amiable faction already, did I need to do all that or would the gnomie have coughed up the Gabstick without it?<br>
<br>
Lascaris<br>
56 wizzie<br>
Fennnin Ro <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ujerrek.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jerrek</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/12/01 6:16:23 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Now that I turned in my 1KPP, did I have to?</span><hr size=1> I think the 2k &quot;investment&quot; is strictly to raise Truespirit.  If you were amiable already, you could probably have skipped that entire portion.<br>
<br>
Anyone notice how the wiz epic really lacks a story?  All of the other epics I've read about have a deeply involved story.. but the wizard one.. blah.<br>
<br>
&quot;Ack you found me, I was cool once, hung out with Sol Ro and all.. but now I'm in hiding.. go find my buddies' staves and bring them to me.  Ok here you go.&quot;<br>
<br>
That's about it. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ufeynanthewizard.showPublicProfile?language=EN>FeynantheWizard</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/12/01 7:45:32 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Now that I turned in my 1KPP, did I have to?</span><hr size=1> i thought you had to turn in 1kpp, not 2kpp?<br>
