<br>
Lascaris <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uemirikal.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Emirikal</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/12/01 9:18:11 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Now that I turned in my 1KPP, did I have to?</span><hr size=1> Well I just turned in the 1k to camin the other night.  I have everything now for the quest except the oil, which is reletively easy.  I was at indiff to truespirit, as I had done the note a few times in the early days.  I think I could have skipped the 1k.  <br>
<br>
But heres the deal.  After 18 phinny kills, numerous tolapumj kills (back when that was still needed I got powder from him,) multiple VS kills (althoug the staff drops a lot) is it worth trying to save 1k pp?  I only had 4k total in the bank, but for me it wasnt worth the risk.  The thought of doing phinny over and over again just wasnt appealing.  pay the money!  besides just think of how much you will save on peridots =)<br>
<br>
Emirikal<br>
Sorcerer of L`Malla<br>
Druzzil Ro <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.showMessage?topicID=1475.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.showMessage?topicID=1457.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.emailToFriend?topicID=1479.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.threadControl?topicID=1479.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1479.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1479.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm4">Rant Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm8">Mob Dropped Spells<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm10">Class Balance & Class Bugs<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm38">Discussion of Inter-Species Tension<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm22">Out o